Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸计划 进入第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是移民计划失败的受害者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遗弃在火星圈的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在严酷环境下生活的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回那座名为「地球」的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策划起了规模宏大的计划
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A.G.140年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「驱蝠战役」后25年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦与火星圈国家维甘的战争仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对维甘日渐扩大的势力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正紧锣密鼓地准备着大规模反击战役
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么？ 艾伦格雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ader的试运行实验前些天完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性能出色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它立即服役的呼声非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ader是在高达AGE-1的基础上设计完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先配备给前线部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是在构思作战计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么滴水不漏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找出维甘的所有藏身地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们赶出这个宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争 还会持续多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说战争的开端 「天使陨落」事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰巧是司令出生的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40年了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府多次提出过议和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们却一概拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有正常人的逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与他们谈和是对牛弹琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令还是认为 必须将维甘彻底剿灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是全人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令拥有灵活的判断力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独在这一点上却毫不退让
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说这始终是个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我的想法错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你是斯莱斯雷兹军校首席毕业生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么应该明白作为参谋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须积极理解司令官的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点不用我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 这次休假是和家人团聚？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆…不知道他现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你们是什么机动战士社团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天在校舍后面吱吱咔咔的烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吵知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们是经过学校同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是找碴来要钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多余的零花钱不如拿出来大家分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只有旧式人工智能芯片级的智商
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想来要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子不想活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为所有人都怕你们就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仗着自己是联邦军司令的儿子 嚣张是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你知道什么叫后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师如果没来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆早把他们打得四脚朝天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 学校里打架没好果子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 他们可能还会来报复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再扁一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动了动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威！马希尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 大概是手腕的驱动控制系统还有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啊大哥 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 刚才的声音好吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们的…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽·斯通主动和我们说话！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能造出这样的东西太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机…机动战士方面是我们的强项
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽 小心弄脏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一股机油味 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽还是那么可爱 啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被机动战士缠身的家族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你还记着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 尤诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真难得 爸爸能赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 上次是什么时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特现在是联邦军的司令官了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能总是放下军务陪着家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 17岁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 麻烦再来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 吃得太多可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 外公太贪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤诺亚怎么也说我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第三盘而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是明日野家族世代相传的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野家族世代相传…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆迟早必须继承它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久自然会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会保护你 和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕 便宜都给哥哥占了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时时刻刻都要带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我会保管好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论发生什么 你也要保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是明日野家族继承者的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 下周有机动战士大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他们在为卫冕做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 假期只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就必须出门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给斯莱斯雷兹军校写推荐信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精英学校不好读
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就要用功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 想让我当军人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班级又有了新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是杰哈特·葛雷德同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以走在走廊正中间的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是那个转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是洛德阿布斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教会你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所学校的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 初来乍到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 明白了就好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部分和其他关键驱动没有形成联动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把转力控制程序换成先前的版本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要换的话 其他关节也得换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备份在哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的版本？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那版本也有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣加入机动战士社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看条件差 去年还得了托尔迪亚冠军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已掌握进入卫星的路径
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腕的动作还是没有改进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要求太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重写关节驱动程序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周后就比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想输给德鲁斯缇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想输！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 你这是在急什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得冠军 被老爸的认可是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得已经很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…不是因为那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在格斗大赛上夺冠 没什么错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急避难警报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈明明说托尔迪亚戒备森严不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是居民区的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去大家都会遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 妈妈的电话也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把脚扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去 我和家里人联系不上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆　这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 尤诺亚她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 和艾米莉一起到地下避难…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她受伤了 不能丢下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔瑟 汉斯 咋样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是菲利特制造出的最强机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的机动战士竟然在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 菲利特那小子故意藏在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护这座卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它去…作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸知道会有这么一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 到关键时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须承担起保护大家的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是明日野家族的男人的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会保护你和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会和爸爸那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 我决定干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就能动？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常维护从没有怠慢过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达的性能远远胜过菲利特当年用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 开动它的话马厩不会塌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别操心 乔瑟！汉斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE装置就是钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来它就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心着点 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士的基本操作我全掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主监视器点亮 能量系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来！ 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚瑟姆在驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是高达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行 我能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有上 我必须保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 看我一定干掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 二刀流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇静 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇静 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那个机师让人感觉稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了 赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两台Dorado 就这么完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是高达的性能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这雾是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达从视野中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于还是开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让你品尝到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去宝贵的人的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆　高达就托付给你了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
